	<package>
		<name>MacOS Microsoft Windows App</name>
		<application_name>Windows App</application_name>
		<bundleId>com.microsoft.rdc.macos</bundleId>
		<currentVersionReleaseDate>June 29, 2026</currentVersionReleaseDate>
		<icon_image>https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/dd/48/06/dd480661-3a03-60fb-bfeb-5ce84b615d0f/AppIcon-0-0-85-220-0-0-6-0-2x.png/512x512bb.png</icon_image>
		<minimumOsVersion>14.0</minimumOsVersion>
		<releaseNotes>In this release we made the following updates:

• Added a new Personalization section (under Settings) to customize how the app looks and feels.
• Updated the Quick Launcher to make it detachable, resizable and independent from the Connection Center lifetime.
• Moved the Search control from the sidebar to the toolbar, and reordered the toolbar items.
• Updated the First Run Experience and permission request dialogs.
• Resolved an issue where tab navigation on the sidebar wasn't working after the app was launched.
• Corrected default device card thumbnail aspect ratios that could become distorted after resizing the Connection Center.
• Fixed a bug that caused the Settings dialog to not open in the current active space.
• Adjusted the default size of the Connection Center for macOS 26+.
• Optimized device card thumbnail rendering performance in the Connection Center.
• Improved app responsiveness by coalescing workspace update-triggered UI refreshes.
• Made updates to improve Continuous Access Evaluation (CAE) scenarios for AVD and Windows 365.
• Resolved app crashes and hangs.

If you encounter any errors, you can contact us via Help &gt; Submit Feedback.</releaseNotes>
		<version>11.3.7</version>
		<app_store_url>https://apps.apple.com/us/app/windows-app/id1295203466?mt=12&amp;uo=4</app_store_url>
